(Republished)

Rodney G. Kirkland, an Infant, by His Guardian ad Litem, Pearl Kirkland, et al., Appellants, v. City of New York et al., Respondents.

Judgment unanimously affirmed, with $50 costs to respondents. No opinion. The order of this court [24 A D 2d 555] entered on June 8, 1965 is vacated. Concur—Botein, P. J., Rabin, McNally, Stevens and Eager, JJ.
